name: Utopia
description:
Law and order, everything goes to plan, everything is very well thought of.

It’s a Utopian concept that doesn’t exist in my small island of Bali. That is why when I visited Japan for the very first time, I am intrigued in how everything just falls perfectly into place. A life where everyday moves in patterns and repetitions.

 The thing is, people may not enjoy queueing or living like robots, but over there.. they still do it.
